sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant S as Server
    participant SM as SessionManager
    participant DB as SQLite

    B->>S: POST /api/session/login username+password
    S->>SM: loginUser(username, password)
    SM->>DB: findUserByUsername(username)
    DB-->>SM: user row with passwordHash and passwordSalt
    SM->>SM: scrypt hash comparison via timingSafeEqual
    SM->>SM: randomBytes(32) generates token stored in Map
    SM-->>S: token and user object
    S->>B: Set-Cookie synchro_session=TOKEN HttpOnly SameSite=Strict Max-Age=43200

    Note over B,S: Subsequent requests carry the cookie automatically

    B->>S: GET /api/admin/keys with cookie
    S->>SM: requireSession(req)
    SM->>SM: Parse cookie and look up token in Map
    SM->>DB: findUserById to re-hydrate fresh user data
    SM->>SM: Extend expiresAt by 12 hours sliding window
    SM-->>S: session object with user and permissions
    S-->>B: 200 OK with keys array
